- app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/MediaController.php

Explanation:
- The App\Http\Controllers\Api\V1\MediaController@destroy handler is implemented in this file.
- The method signature is destroy(Media $medium): Response, relying on route-model binding for the {media} parameter.
- It performs authorization with $this->authorize('delete', $medium), then calls $medium->delete(), and returns a 204 No Content response via response()->noContent().
- The route in routes/api.php maps the DELETE request to /v1/media/{media} to this destroy method (through the apiResource('media', MediaController::class)->only(['store', 'destroy']) configuration).
